The Focus RS build is a global collaboration between Ford Performance, Block’s Hoonigan Racing Division and U.K.-based M-Sport. Featuring all-wheel drive, a new EcoBoost® engine producing 600 horsepower, and a 0-60 mph launch time of less than two seconds, the Ford Focus RS RX is optimized for rallycross competition.
